  .Visit GitHub:URL -n https://github.com/Blasman/mIRC-Twitch-Scripts
  $chr(36) $+ $chr(36) $+ $chr(36) CLICK HERE TO DONATE $chr(36) $+ $chr(36) $+ $chr(36):URL -n https://twitch.streamlabs.com/blasman13
